name: Xid-figures
body:
### XID+ Figures
This page contains the full list of triangle figures for all 360 Herschel sources described in Scudder et al (2016, MNRAS submitted).  Each figure contains the full posterior distribution for each potential component's flux.

### Author
This page is maintained by @jmscudder.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
